items.title: Nandini retains fourth spot in food, beverages category among Indian Brands, Amul leads: Report
items.description: Nandini has retained its fourth position, standing alongside leading brands such as Amul (#1), Mother Dairy (#2), Britannia (#3) and Dabur (#5)

items.title: Efforts ongoing to serve legal documents to Gautam Adani, Sagar Adani in bribery case: US SEC
items.description: SEC said it is continuing to pursue formal service of the summons and complaint under the provisions of the Hague Service Convention
